                                <date>1958</date>. С. <biblScope unit="page">??–??</biblScope>.</bibl></sourceDesc></fileDesc><encodingDesc><tagsDecl>&amp;renditions;</tagsDecl></encodingDesc></teiHeader><text><body><entry xml:id="entry_ægærc" xml:lang="os"><form xml:lang="os-x-iron" type="lemma"><orth>ægærc</orth></form><form xml:lang="os-x-digor" type="dialectal"><orth>ægærcæ</orth><form type="variant"><orth>igærcæ</orth></form></form><re><form xml:lang="os-x-iron" type="lemma"><orth>gom-ægærccæj</orth></form><form xml:lang="os-x-digor" type="dialectal"><orth>igon-igærcæj</orth></form><sense><tr xml:lang="ru"><q>нагишом</q></tr><tr xml:lang="en"><q>naked</q></tr></sense></re><exampleGrp><example><quote>æz dæ fædyl wajyn gom-ægærccæj</quote><tr xml:lang="ru"><q>я бегу за тобой нагишом</q></tr><tr xml:lang="en"><q>I'm running naked after you</q></tr><bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Niger"/><biblScope>154</biblScope></bibl></example></exampleGrp><exampleGrp><example><quote>æz dæ fædyl wajyn gom-ægærccæj</quote><tr xml:lang="ru"><q>я бегу за тобой нагишом</q></tr><tr xml:lang="en"><q>I'm running naked after you</q></tr><bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Niger"/><biblScope>154</biblScope></bibl></example></exampleGrp><etym xml:lang="ru">Из %iæ-kærc%i ‘без шубы’. ‘Отсутствие шубы’ как синоним ‘наготы’ указывает на жизнь в суровом климате. Начальное %ii%i в д. %iigærcæ%i -— перебойное из %iæ%i; ср. %iidonug%i рядом с <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ædonug"/> ‘жажда’ и др. См. также под <ref type="xr" target="#entry_gom"/>.</etym><etym xml:lang="en">From %iæ-kærc%i ‘without fur coat’. ‘Absence of fur coat’ synonymous to ‘nudity’ indicates life in a harsh climate. The initial %ii%i in Digor %iigærcæ%i alternates with %iæ%i; cf. %iidonug%i from <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ædonug"/> ‘thirst’ etc. See also under <ref type="xr" target="#entry_gom"/>.</etym></entry></body></text></TEI>